snippet.title: PC Longplay [712] Rick Dangerous II
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: SCHLAUCHI

Almost as good as the Amiga version!
I was too lazy to edit out one of the deaths in the mines, so its not a completely flawless run!

Due to an error in the original video I had to replace the footage between 00:19:50 and 00:20:12 which is the reason why the score changes! -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
